Phrase: Nen-nen-korori, nen-korori.\nThe doll with big ears.\nLet's pat your head.
In place of my daughter.\nPlease play with the crows.
Nen-nen-korori, nen-korori.\nThe doll with beautiful hair.\nLet's pretty you up.
Before the dawn.\nTake your pain somewhere else.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan, Yoshino-chan...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...mmmm, Miyako?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Thank goodness. It seems my protection incantations are stronger.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Is this... Ningyo Jigoku?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What is this place? Is there such a scary place?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: There's a place like this in Iris Cloud's Nishiki. But we can't see it on our normal life.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Maybe we fell into the interstellar world, or maybe it's a recreation of Yoshino-chan's memories.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan, is your body alright? Do you remember what happened in the cave?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: I remember. We found some nagashi-bina and Miyako came up with a great theory.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What happened a bit later?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino heard someone's voice. I can't remember what she sounded like, but she was calling Yoshino's name.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: After that, Yakky-tan and friends got upset with me...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako grabbed me and Yoshino fell down and hit my head...?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino, you didn't hit your head, you landed on your butt.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooh- it was on the butt? No wonder Yoshino's tail is all messed up.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Your fur is dishevelled because Yoshino-chan jumped into the water.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oh no, Yoshino is not Putra.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, that's why Putra-san was so surprised.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: For real?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I guess you don't remember everything. I thought you would at least remember the doll.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Doll?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: The black doll that Yoshino-chan protected so dearly.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh, No memory of this at all.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Why is she all black? The dolls in the cave wore vermillion kimono and white masks, right?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I don't understand. I didn't realise there was such a girl either. It was Yoshino-chan who found her.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino found her? Even Miyako couldn't find her?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: 'Yes, Yoshino-chan found her. You went straight for the doll. You grabbed the doll and was going to use sorcery right away.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Is this also because of the curse? Yoshino almost got everyone involved. Miyako, thank you for saving me.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It's only natural. It's my role to help people.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Hey, Yoshino-chan? Where did you learn that kind of magic?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Eh?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It's the art Yoshino-chan was trying to use before you jumped into the water. Does the Iris Cloud army teach such a forbidden art? Even if Yoshino-chan is a good sorceress, you shouldn't use something like that.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: What kind of art was Yoshino trying to use?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: The art of giving life. You were trying to grant everything that was there life.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You were trying to give life to the water, to the earth, to the dolls. Maybe it wasn't strictly true, but that's probably how it was done.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino doesn't know the art of bringing dolls to life. But... do know the art awaken something that is sleeping or revive something that has withered.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: When Yoshino was in the mountains, learnt this technique to make the sakura bloom. Yoshino made the sakura bloom earlier than they were supposed to bloom. Wanted to use the art learnt at that time in a different way.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino knew not to do it. But still used it. Yoshino was still a small child. At that time, Yoshino was so weak, thinking that death will come soon.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You can make a cherry tree bloom before its supposed to... That's not an art a small child can do. ...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Someone tried to use Yoshino's power. Perhaps the purson who put the curse on Yoshino wanted to revitalise the nagashi-bina that was over there.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The hina were all tired. Yoshino's sure it was after being migawari. So that's why that someone wanted to do something about it.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Using warped powers do not make the dolls healthy. On the contrary, they can be transformed into something terrible.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That's right... It was the same with Nene.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Nene?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The doll who went berserk in Iris Cloud. She was Yoshino's favourite friend's sister.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Your friend's sister was... I'm sorry to hear that.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Don't you think it's weird?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Weird? Was there anything weird about what you just said? Your friend's sister went off the rails with her warped powers, didn't she?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Isn't it weird to have a doll as a friend?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I don't think so. My first friend was a doll too.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino really loves you, Miyako.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What's wrong? That's so sudden. I like Yoshino-chan too, you know?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: What kind of girl was Miyako's friend? How did you come to like dolls?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm a bit different from ordinary people. It's a long story if I tell you all about it...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I grew up in a place that was like a doll dumping ground, in the house of a person who would take in any kind of doll. Dolls with defects gather here from all over M. Nishiki.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: By 'defects' do you mean like 'cursed dolls'?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, yes, exactly.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But actually, cursed dolls don't happen that often, you know? It is always people who cursed them. It's people who hate and resent people. Because dolls love people.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh- the person who made Nene out of control said the same thing.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Then that person really understands dolls.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yes, she knows them well, and likely she loves them. She puts her life on the line for the dolls. That's the kind of person she is.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: That's why one sometimes relies on distorted powers. Goshujin-sama was like that too.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Why do they try to rely on distorted power? Can't they see that it will end badly?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It's because it's something that can't be replaced by human life, that's what I think.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Dolls are made by human hands, aren't they? They are rarely treated as equal to human life. Some people say otherwise, but most people can't put doll's lives on the same scale as their own living children's.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: My friend risked her own life to save me, who's a living being. She was the smartest doll in the house. She could speak and walk on her own two feet.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: If it wasn't for her, I would be dead by now. She saved my life. Thanks to her, I became a living person. I was able to leave Hinayashiki and meet Yae-san.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: This Yae-san is Miyako's shishou?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, she is. She helped me with my old dolls. She gave me thread, scissors and a place to stay. She was a famous local dollmaster.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: So she's like the Somei-Ya to Yoshino. Yoshino was helped by the Someiya couple after I made the cherry blossoms bloom.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: The cherry blossoms told Yoshino to 'live'. Just like Miyabi told me to...

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: There is no time to waste, you two. You two must get out of here quickly and look for the black torii.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Hello. The person who looks good in a fox mask.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Do not let go of that doll. You will need it to save Nishiki. You can keep it forever.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooooh? Wouldn't Miyako be better off with it than Yoshino?

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: No, not Miyako. That doll has been waiting for you for a long time.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Since when has it been waiting for me?

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Ever since the Guardian of the Giant Tree left the Giant Tree of M. Nishiki.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: In case you're wondering, Yoshino is from Iris Cloud.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Iris Cloud and Iris Metro are connected by the Giant Trees. There's nothing strange about that.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: This girl is a bit different. She chooses her owners and leads them where she wants to go. She will show you where you're going until you've done your job...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Is it safe to have this doll? She's not just a decorative doll, is she? She's quiet now, but earlier she tried to use Yoshino's power. She tried to bring the nagashi-bina to life.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: That girl is not dangerous. She is not the one who put the curse on Yoshino, nor the one who tried to use Yoshino's power. She will lead us to the person who put the curse on her.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Yoshino and Miyako. With the power of the two of you, I'm sure you can save that person.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: Aim for the summit. Save the master of this mountain and oka-san.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: She's gone.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I don't know if she's friend or foe, but I didn't sense any evil force.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I mean, she really doesn't show any sign of life until she showed herself.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako sensed someone else, and not her...?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Is that person on the summit?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino, the doll is...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It's alright. Yoshino's not acting weird this time. Still the same Yoshino.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: If what she says is true. This doll has something to do with the Guardian of the Giant Tree.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The doll-san who will take us where you want to go. Hopefully the place you want to go is near the Guardian of the Giant Tree.

Name: Putra
Phrase: YOSHINO!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Thank goodness! Miyako is safe too!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooh-? Everyone's together. Shashou is genki too.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Yoshino is back to normal! Is the curse gone now then?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Probably not. But became friends with this black doll.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: YOU IDIOT! WHAT ARE YA SO GOOFY ABOUT!? You suddenly went mad and jumped into the water and... I'm so worried about you!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh, yoshi yoshi. Yoshino doesn't know what happened, but everything's fine.
It seems that the strange things that happened to Yoshino have stopped. I don't know what happened over there, but I'm glad that we all made it out of the cave safely.

Name: Fox Masked Girl
Phrase: ...You can do it. Good luck.
